    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sanctae et individuae trinitatis. <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/7">Otto</persName> divina favente clementia <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> augustus. Si sanctorum dei ecclesiis
                        ex nostris rebus aliquid offerimus, presentis et aeternae vite bravium
                        adipisci non titubamus. Quapropter omnium sancte dei ecclesie fidelium
                        nostrorumque presentium ac futurorum industria noverit, qualiter pro dei
                        amore animeque nostre remedio quandam <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs> in
                        honore <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1451">sancte Marie</orgName> constructam in
                            <placeName ref="#places/2721">monte Ionio</placeName> sitam cum omnibus
                        rebus et <rs key="#Royal_slave">familiis</rs> ad eam in integrum
                        pertinentibus nec non et <rs key="#Landed_possessions">campum</rs> iuxta
                        eandem ecclesiam regie potestati actenus pertinentem atque <geogName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2351">Barbaritanos</geogName> similiter <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property">iuris regni nostri</rs> pertinentes cum omnibus
                        eorum pertinentiis, insuper et omnem illam terram quam <persName
                            key="#Queen" ref="#people/1524">Berta</persName>
                        <rs key="#Queen">regina</rs> ex <geogName ref="#estates/1406"
                            >Camerino</geogName> adquisivit in <rs key="#Mountains">monte
                            Ferentino</rs>, atque <rs key="#Landed_possessions">sortem</rs> de
                            <geogName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2355">Lauro</geogName> et <geogName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2352">Muglani</geogName> que regie parti pertinuit,
                        insuper etiam <rs key="#Churches">capellam</rs> in honore <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >sancti Marini</orgName> constructam cum suis pertinentiis atque <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">sortem</rs> in <geogName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2353">querceto</geogName> que laboratur per
                                <persName><name ref="Bonipertus">Bonipertum</name></persName> quam
                            <persName ref="#people/1516">Boso</persName> eidem contulit
                        congregationi, per huius nostri precepti paginam <rs key="#Monks"
                            >monachis</rs> et confratribus in <rs key="#Monasteries">cenobio</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1450"
                            key="#Mansi #Landed_possessions #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium #Churches #Monasteries"
                            >sancte Flore</orgName> deo famulantibus nec non
                            <placeName>[Ve]lsam</placeName> et <placeName>Ursicinum</placeName> et
                            <rs key="#Mansi">mansum</rs> in <placeName>Garsiniano</placeName> et <rs
                            key="#Mansi">mansum</rs> in <placeName>[M]aiana</placeName> in usum et
                        sumptum illorum concedimus donamus atque largimur et <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >de nostro iure et dominio in eorum ius et dominium</rs> omnimodis
                        tranfundimus ac delegamus, ut in illorum stipendium predicta predia maneant
                        ipsique habeant teneant firmiterque possideant posterique illorum iure
                        perpetuo. Insuper etiam <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terram</rs>
                        <geogName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2354">Martinensem</geogName> cum omnibus suis pertinentiis
                        nec non omnes res et familias quas constructor eiusdem loci prefato cenobio
                        contulit, et cuncta ab aliis conlata fidelibus per hoc idem preceptum
                        concedimus confirmamus et corroboramus ipsius cenobii fratribus et tam
                        monachos quamque illorum familiam et <rs key="#Agricultural_workers"
                            >massarios</rs> cunctasque res eiusdem cenobii sub nostre <rs
                            key="#Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium">defensionis munburdum</rs> recepimus,
                        precipientes ut nullus dux marchio comes aut quislibet homo predictum
                        cenobium de rebus suis molestare absque legali iudicio audeat. Si quis
                        igitur huius precepti violator extiterit, sciat se compositurum <rs
                            key="#Penalty">auri optimi libras centum</rs>, <rs key="#Camera_regis"
                            >medietatem kamere nostre</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem predicto
                            cenobio</rs>. Quod ut verius credatur, manibus propriis roborantes
                        annulum nostrum subter imprimere iussimus. Signum domni Ottonis (MF.)
                        invigtissimi imperatoris augusti. <persName key="#Chancellor" ref="#people/3962">Heribertus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellari</rs> vice <persName key="#Bishops" ref="#people/223">Petri</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> notavi. (SI. 3.) Data VIII. kal. iun. anno
                        dominice incarnationis DCCCCXCVI, indictione VIIII, anno vero tertii Ottonis
                        regnantis XIII, imperii I; actum <placeName ref="#places/52"
                            >Rome</placeName>; feliciter amen.</ab>
                </div>
